            <p class="mb-4">Don't miss this opportunity to be part of the peace movement.</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/<%= milestone.whatsappNumber %>?text=Hello! I'd like to RSVP for <%= encodeURIComponent(milestone.title) %>" 
